## `NavIcon` forwardRef (`lib/sdui/icons.tsx`)

`NavIcon` is wrapped in `React.forwardRef` using an `inline-flex span` as the ref target:

```tsx
export const NavIcon = React.forwardRef<HTMLSpanElement, NavIconProps>(
  function NavIcon(props, ref) {
    return (
      <span ref={ref} style={{ display: 'inline-flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
        <IconComponent ... />
      </span>
    );
  }
);
```

This ensures `data-builder-id` is set on the span so icons are selectable/resizable in the builder.

